                    <p class="footer-description">© 2026 QueuePro. All rights reserved.</p>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 0.25rem;">Surat District Citizen Service
                        Center</p>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-links">
                    <div class="footer-column">
