                    <p style="color: #e5e7eb; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
                        <strong style="color: #ffc107;">Disclaimer:</strong> This system assists queue scheduling. It
                        does not replace official government processes. For legal matters, please visit the office in
                        person with valid ID proof.
                    </p>
